		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Heh, kind of off-topic but when I was using Squeedo through the RS232, I got a real kick out of displaying color ANSI graphics on the PC terminal.  The Squeedo control menu suddenly felt like an old dial-up BBS. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif" alt=":D" title="Very Happy" />  Unfortunately, I wanted to stick with monochrome so the NES PPU could display it.

		

